## Patching

Review [kured Releases](https://github.com/kubereboot/charts/releases) page to check for breaking changes.

[Example PR for upgrading version](https://github.com/hmcts/cnp-flux-config/pull/29413)

Similarly, create a PR in sds-flux-config to patch kured in SDS.  Please note that in SDS environment, kured is deployed under admin namespace.

### Checks to see if upgrade worked correctly
After above raised PR approved and merged, describe the kured pod on different clusters and check the labels has updated kured chart version.
e.g.

```bash
kubectl describe pod <POD NAME> -n kured | grep "helm.sh/chart"

```
